snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Darktide – New Announcements
snippet.description:
Rejects, rejoice! There's new DLC inbound for the frenetic first-person co-op shooter! Plus, the game is soon making its long-awaited debut on PS5 – learn more: https://www.warhammer-community.com/en-gb/articles/hqa4mcq8/return-to-the-corrupted-carnival-in-the-next-free-update-for-warhammer-40000-darktide/
